      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and I'd love to see it go to a great home. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and still has so much life left in it! It runs super smoothly and has been really well-loved and looked after over the years. It's the perfect fit if you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for its next big adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014I just know you're going to love how it handles!",
