    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "For sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit, ensuring the structural and mechanical integrity of the chassis. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, with bushings recently inspected for compliance. The engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline with no evidence of rod bearing fatigue. While the aesthetic condition shows light patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight and the throttle mapping is exceptionally responsive. A superb entry for the purist seeking a tactile, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
