    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between everyday utility and refined comfort. The exterior retains a brilliant shine, with the paintwork showing only the minor, superficial character marks one would expect from a vehicle that has been driven and enjoyed responsibly. All glass is clear and free of chips, and the alloy wheels are in great shape. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment. The leather upholstery remains supple and supportive, while the dashboard and touchpoints show minimal wear. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control and the power sunroof, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly through the gears of the smooth-shifting automatic transmission. I have kept a rigorous maintenance schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The tires have significant tread depth remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a dependable, honest car that has been treated with respect and is ready to provide its next owner with years of reliable service.",
